CH -- Non issue.  PoP designed for it, and hardly has any effect at all now.  A Warrior would need to have 9375 hps to not make it to full hps after a CH at one bub left.  If some Wars with 8k hps, aren't making it to full bar after getting a CH with a tiny fraction of a bub of hps left, then who cares.  And this is the CH with no AA or focus effect working behind it.  The tank would have to have a lot more hps to not make full bar from 1 bub if the Cleric has any AA or focus.<br>
